          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", but one of those hotbeds is Las Vegas, Nevada. Per a local report, Las Vegas Metropolitan Police say so far in 2023 1,485 cars have been stolen or broken into. That’s in just two months. Keep in mind the Las Vegas metro population is just 2.8 million.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
